00:34:41.643 --> 00:34:42.119
means.
 

00:34:42.119 --> 00:34:47.391
When you multiply the
derivative by some dx,

00:34:47.391 --> 00:34:49.289
what do you get?
 

00:34:49.289 --> 00:34:49.789
Pardon me?
 

00:34:49.789 --> 00:34:51.190
Yes, go ahead.
 

00:34:51.190 --> 00:34:52.099
